{"data":{"html":{"path":"/html/style","title":"Cara Memberi Style pada Elemen HTML","content":"<h1 id=\"cara-memberi-style-pada-elemen-html\"><a href=\"#cara-memberi-style-pada-elemen-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Cara Memberi Style pada Elemen HTML</h1>\n<p>Apa jadinya kalau membuat halaman website hanya menggunakan HTML saja?</p>\n<p>Ya kamu benar sekali, tampilannya akan berantakan dan tidak menarik sama sekali.</p>\n<p>Karena urusan mempercantik halaman website itu sudah menjadi tugasnya CSS.</p>\n<p>Lalu bagaimana caranya memberi style pada elemen HTML dengan CSS?</p>\n<h2 id=\"gunakan-atribut-style-pada-element-html\"><a href=\"#gunakan-atribut-style-pada-element-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Gunakan Atribut Style pada Element HTML</h2>\n<p>Untuk memberi style pada elemen HTML kamu bisa menggunakan atribut <code class=\"language-text\">style</code> yang diletakkan pada tag pembuka elemen HTML.</p>\n<p>Begini sintaks penulisannya:</p>\n<pre class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>tagname</span><span class=\"token style-attr language-css\"><span class=\"token attr-name\"> <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=\"</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token property\">property</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></pre>\n<p><strong>Property</strong> menunjukkan properti CSS, sedangkan <strong>value</strong> menunjukkan nilai CSS dari properti tersebut.</p>\n<h2 id=\"cara-memberi-warna-teks-pada-html\"><a href=\"#cara-memberi-warna-teks-pada-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Cara Memberi Warna Teks pada HTML</h2>\n<p>Setelah tahu cara penggunaan atribut style, sekarang saatnya menerapkan properti dan value css untuk mengatur style elemen HTML.</p>\n<p>Yuk kita mulai dengan memberi warna teks judul dan paragraf pada dokumen HTML.</p>\n<p>Caranya dengan memakai properti <code class=\"language-text\">color</code> pada atribut style. Perhatikan contoh berikut:</p>\n<pre class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token style-attr language-css\"><span class=\"token attr-name\"> <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=\"</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>blue<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Ini Judul dengan Warna Biru<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token style-attr language-css\"><span class=\"token attr-name\"> <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=\"</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Ini paragraf pertama dengan warna merah.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token style-attr language-css\"><span class=\"token attr-name\"> <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=\"</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>green<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Ini paragraf kedua dengan warna hijau.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></pre>\n<p>Begini tampilannya di web browser!</p>\n<h1 style=\"color:blue;\">Ini Judul dengan Warna Biru</h1>\n<p style=\"color:red;\">Ini paragraf pertama dengan warna merah.</p>\n<p style=\"color:green;\">Ini paragraf kedua dengan warna hijau.</p>\n<h2 id=\"cara-memberi-background-pada-html\"><a href=\"#cara-memberi-background-pada-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Cara Memberi Background pada HTML</h2>\n<p>Untuk memberi warna background pada elemen HTML, gunakanlah properti css <code class=\"language-text\">background-color</code> pada atribut style.</p>\n<p>Pada contoh berikut saya memberi background berwarna biru langit pada elemen <code class=\"language-text\">div</code>:</p>\n<pre class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token style-attr language-css\"><span class=\"token attr-name\"> <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=\"</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>powderblue<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Ini Judul Pertama Saya<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Ini paragraf pertama saya.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></pre>\n<p><a href=\"/text-editor\">Coba Praktek</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"cara-mengatur-ukuran-teks-pada-html\"><a href=\"#cara-mengatur-ukuran-teks-pada-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Cara Mengatur Ukuran Teks pada HTML</h2>\n<p>Untuk mengatur ukuran teks pada elemen HTML, maka gunakanlah properti css <code class=\"language-text\">font-size</code> pada atribut style.</p>\n<p>Lihat contoh ini:</p>\n<pre class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token style-attr language-css\"><span class=\"token attr-name\"> <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=\"</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>42px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Ini Judul Pertama Saya<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token style-attr language-css\"><span class=\"token attr-name\"> <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=\"</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>20px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Ini paragraf pertama saya.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></pre>\n<p>Begini tampilannya di web browser!</p>\n<h1 style=\"font-size:42px;\">Ini Judul Pertama Saya</h1>\n<p style=\"font-size:20px;\">Ini paragraf pertama saya.</p>\n<h2 id=\"cara-mengatur-rata-teks-pada-html\"><a href=\"#cara-mengatur-rata-teks-pada-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Cara Mengatur Rata Teks pada HTML</h2>\n<p>Untuk mengatur rata teks pada elemen HTML, maka gunakanlah properti css <code class=\"language-text\">text-align</code> pada atribut style.</p>\n<p>Contoh:</p>\n<pre class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token style-attr language-css\"><span class=\"token attr-name\"> <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=\"</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token property\">text-align</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Ini paragraf dengan rata kiri.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token style-attr language-css\"><span class=\"token attr-name\"> <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=\"</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token property\">text-align</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>center</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Ini paragraf dengan rata tengah.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token style-attr language-css\"><span class=\"token attr-name\"> <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=\"</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token property\">text-align</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>right</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Ini paragraf dengan rata kanan.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></pre>\n<p>Begini tampilannya di web browser!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left\">Ini paragraf dengan rata kiri.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">Ini paragraf dengan rata tengah.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right\">Ini paragraf dengan rata kanan.</p>\n","headings":[{"value":"Cara Memberi Style pada Elemen HTML"}],"subtitles":[{"value":"Gunakan Atribut Style pada Element HTML","anchor":"#gunakan-atribut-style-pada-element-html"},{"value":"Cara Memberi Warna Teks pada HTML","anchor":"#cara-memberi-warna-teks-pada-html"},{"value":"Cara Memberi Background pada HTML","anchor":"#cara-memberi-background-pada-html"},{"value":"Cara Mengatur Ukuran Teks pada HTML","anchor":"#cara-mengatur-ukuran-teks-pada-html"},{"value":"Cara Mengatur Rata Teks pada HTML","anchor":"#cara-mengatur-rata-teks-pada-html"}]}},"context":{}}